652
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:40,400
Your heir involves Nine Cities.

653
00:36:40,530 --> 00:36:42,620
It's not just a personal matter.

654
00:36:44,170 --> 00:36:45,830
Among all the world's charms,

655
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:46,970
