656
00:36:47,820 --> 00:36:48,530
Besides,

657
00:36:48,530 --> 00:36:50,330
I already have my wife by my side.

658
00:36:50,610 --> 00:36:51,670
I'm afraid my heart

659
00:36:51,790 --> 00:36:53,320
